{"tid":1140041,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"WWE集中討論區","createTime":"2019-05-05T15:52:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-10T17:43:09.000Z","uid":191650,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"2e8264871e768f2bb3552414094fd1f86197ec3d","tid":1140041,"uid":191650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T15:52:00.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">新手必知</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n世界摔角娛樂（英語：World Wrestling Entertainment，品牌名稱：WWE，另譯美國職業摔角），是美國著名職業摔角上市公司<br />\n<br />\n旗下主節目分為<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">RAW</span></span> <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">Smackdown live</span></span> <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">NXT</span></span><br />\n<br />\nRAW為美國時間星期一播放<br />\nWWE Raw一次就播出三個小時<br />\nSmackdown live為美國時間星期二播放<br />\nWWE smackdown live 一次就播出兩小時<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港想睇可以用NowTV或Viutvsix</span><br />\n<br />\n歡迎任何對WWE 有興趣或啱啱接觸嘅人討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">目前選手名單及腰帶持有者</span><br />\n<br />\n腰帶持有者<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/i22xaCT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fi22xaCT.png&h=d9282256&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zK2ASRe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzK2ASRe.png&h=33676fc0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nRAW選手<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/quSpMbB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FquSpMbB.png&h=3f361bcf&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YPZ7JYh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYPZ7JYh.png&